data.description: Cute ranch home with tons of updates such as a new roof, new gutters, new furnace and new AC! It is located near library, shopping centers, restaurants, schools and has easy access to major highways and interstate. This perry township home comes with 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, attached 2 car garage, corian countertops in spacious kitchen with pantry, large WIC in primary bedroom, and a large stone patio in the fenced backyard. Large great room. A must see.
